snippet.title: Solitude Teaser Trailer 4K
snippet.description:
Solitude coming soon in 2024 on Steam 

Survive on a haunted island, facing ancient evil forces. Battle night horrors, build shelters, scavenge for supplies, and unravel the island's mystery.

Wishlist now: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2603400/Solitude/ 

Join our Discord & Subreddit for more information 

Discord: https://discord.gg/w2r8GRbk

Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/SolitudeSurvival/
